    title: "Hello, Penguins"
    format: html
    execute:
      echo: false
    ---
    ```

-   `## Write with **Markdown**`

    **RStudio**: Help \> Markdown Quick Reference

    RStudio & VS Code: Use the **Visual Editor**

    ``` markdown
